00:03:23.750 --> 00:03:28.370
And in a lot of cases developers
and website managers also have

00:03:28.370 --> 00:03:30.080
to deal with emails.

00:03:30.080 --> 00:03:31.910
So there are transactional emails.

00:03:35.380 --> 00:03:40.660
These are commonly the notifications
that we get when someone registers

00:03:40.660 --> 00:03:45.190
on your website,
or sends a contact message,

00:03:45.190 --> 00:03:48.670
or buys something from
your e-commerce website.

00:03:48.670 --> 00:03:52.620
So these are called transactional
emails and these are usually built in

00:03:52.620 --> 00:03:56.930
with themes and plug-ins and
even the WordPress core itself.

00:03:56.930 --> 00:04:00.770
And there are also marketing
emails, and most

00:04:00.770 --> 00:04:03.570
